Two People Killed as Light Plane Crashes in Bulgaria

-- B y   E l i z a b e t h   K o n s t a n t i n o v a
-- 
2011-08-24T16:08:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-24/two-people-killed-as-light-plane-crashes-in-bulgaria-correct-.html
(Corrects type of aircraft in headline.)  Two people were killed when a Cirrus
SR22 plane crashed while trying to land at Primorsko airport
near the Bulgarian Black Sea coast, the Transport Ministry in
Sofia said in an e-mailed statement today.  The small plane with the pilot and a passenger on board
caught fire immediately after the crash, the ministry said. The
accident is being investigated, the ministry said.  To contact the editors responsible for this story:
